Package: NMOF
Type: Package
Title: Functions, data and examples from the book 'Numerical Methods and Optimization in Finance' by M. Gilli, D. Maringer and E. Schumann.
Version: 0.13-1
Date: 2011-06-30
Author: Enrico Schumann
Maintainer: Enrico Schumann <enricoschumann@yahoo.de>
Suggests: MASS, quadprog, RUnit
Description: Functions, code examples and data from the book 'Numerical Methods and Optimization in Finance' by M. Gilli, D. Maringer and E. Schumann. The package contains, in particular, several functions for heuristic optimisation (eg, Differential Evolution, Genetic Algorithms or Threshold Accepting).
